column1: # phase_duration: Duration of current traffic light phase (seconds)
# remaining_duration: Time until next phase change (seconds)
# signal_states: Current state of all signals (g=green
# total_queue_length: Number of stopped vehicles at intersection (vehicles)
# vehicles_stopped: Number of unique vehicles stopped at intersection (vehicles)
# average_waiting_time: Average time vehicles have been waiting (seconds)
# vehicles_by_type: Dictionary of vehicle counts by vehicle type
# lane_to_signal_mapping: Dictionary mapping lanes to their controlling signals
